        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2011-10-27T20:41:09Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Consumer Mobile Fairness Act of 2011 - Renders invalid or unenforceable any pre-dispute arbitration agreement between an individual and a provider of commercial mobile service or mobile broadband Internet access service. Defines a &quot;pre-dispute arbitration agreement&quot; as an agreement to arbitrate a dispute that has not yet arisen at the time of the making of&nbsp;such agreement.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
